sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP TLS (SIMPLE)
    participant KnativeQP as Knative Queue-Proxy<br/>mTLS (Istio)
    participant CaikitHTTP as Caikit HTTP Server<br/>8080/TCP
    participant CaikitGRPC as Caikit gRPC Server<br/>8085/TCP
    participant TGIS as TGIS Backend<br/>8033/TCP localhost
    participant S3 as S3/Minio Storage<br/>9000/TCP
    participant Prom as Prometheus (UWM)<br/>8086/TCP

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: External HTTP Inference Request
    Client->>IstioGW: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS<br/>Auth: Optional (Authorino)
    IstioGW->>KnativeQP: HTTP/8080<br/>mTLS (Istio STRICT)<br/>PeerAuthentication
    KnativeQP->>CaikitHTTP: HTTP/8080<br/>mTLS (Istio STRICT)<br/>PeerAuthentication
    CaikitHTTP->>TGIS: gRPC/8033<br/>plaintext (localhost)<br/>No auth
    TGIS-->>CaikitHTTP: Inference Result
    CaikitHTTP-->>KnativeQP: JSON Response
    KnativeQP-->>IstioGW: Response
    IstioGW-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: External gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>IstioGW: gRPC call caikit.runtime.Nlp<br/>HTTPS (h2)/443, TLS Passthrough<br/>Auth: Optional (Authorino)
    IstioGW->>KnativeQP: gRPC (h2c)/8085<br/>mTLS (Istio STRICT)
    KnativeQP->>CaikitGRPC: gRPC (h2c)/8085<br/>mTLS (Istio STRICT)
    CaikitGRPC->>TGIS: gRPC/8033<br/>plaintext (localhost)
    TGIS-->>CaikitGRPC: Inference Result
    CaikitGRPC-->>KnativeQP: gRPC Response
    KnativeQP-->>IstioGW: Response
    IstioGW-->>Client: gRPC Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Model Loading at Startup
    Note right of S3: KServe Storage Initializer<br/>downloads model artifacts
    S3-->>TGIS: Model artifacts via<br/>/mnt/models volume<br/>S3 API, AWS credentials
    TGIS->>TGIS: Load model weights<br/>from /mnt/models/artifacts/

    Note over Prom,CaikitHTTP: Flow 4: Metrics Scraping
    Prom->>CaikitHTTP: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8086<br/>plaintext (PERMISSIVE mTLS)
    CaikitHTTP-->>Prom: Prometheus Metrics
